      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not required at MRL 2 for this factor category.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency analysis of input parameters between validation and COU scenarios is not required at MRL 2. The close correspondence between validation and COU operating conditions, documented under the test conditions factor, provides sufficient confidence in parameter equivalency."
