    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed the required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are not required at this model risk level given medium model influence and the available experimental validation dataset. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index RH < 1.0 acceptance criterion is satisfied across all evaluated operating points.",
